      • NoteFieldData

        public NoteFieldData(IModelingSession modelingSession,
                     ModelElement me,
                     java.lang.String moduleName,
                     java.lang.String noteTypeName)
        Creates a note field data.

        Notes will be created as HTML if the note type MIME type is HTML, plain text in all other cases.

        Parameters:
        modelingSession - the Modeling session, needed since 3.8 .
        me - the edited element
        moduleName - the note type module
        noteTypeName - the note type module name

        me - the edited element

        noteTypeName - the note type module name
        newNoteType - the new notes MIME type : either "plain" or "html"
